parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag can cause the airbag to rupture, leading to metal fragments passing through the airbag and into the vehicle interior at high speed, which can result in injury or death to vehicle occupants.
symptoms: The airbag warning indicator illuminates
the airbag does not deploy in an accident
the airbag deploys with excessive force
the airbag ruptures
metal fragments are projected into the vehicle interior.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to obtain recall repairs can leave the vehicle in an unsafe condition, putting the occupants at risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The dealer does not have the necessary parts to complete the repair
the dealer cancels the appointment without notification
the manufacturer does not provide a solution to obtain the repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a problem with the airbag system, which can lead to a failure of the airbag to deploy in an accident, resulting in injury or death to vehicle occupants.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates
the airbag system is faulty
the airbag does not deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Subframe Corrosion and Control Arm Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the subframe and failure of the control arm can cause the suspension to detach, leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Abnormal loud grinding sounds coming from underneath the front passenger's side of the vehicle
unknown parts hanging underneath the vehicle
rust holes in the subframe
corrosion of the rear chassis member
and detachment of the front lower control arm at the cross-member.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Recall Repair Delays and Parts Unavailability
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delays and unavailability of parts for recall repairs can leave vehicles in an unsafe condition, putting drivers and passengers at risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Notification of recalls
but parts are unavailable
dealers unable to schedule repairs
and manufacturers exceeding a reasonable amount of time for recall repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rear Subframe and Frame Rail Rust
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting of the rear subframe and frame rails can lead to a catastrophic failure, causing the loss of vehicle control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Rust accumulation on the frame rails
rust holes in the subframe
failure of the rear suspension and drivetrain components
loss of vehicle control.
